12: Having too much fun, I guess...
16:
You need to assert yourself more,
young man. These girls are leading
you around by the nose.
21: Hit the nail on the head, did I?
25:
They are kinda treating me like a
toy, huh?
29:
Perhaps you could see this as an
opportunity and make an advance
of your own?
42:
Hmm? What are you two talking
about over there?
46:
I did not call for you, Princess. Please
go amuse yourself with a starfish or
something.
51:
What did you say?! I am NOT so
easily entertained—
56: Inaho, look. A large sea cucumber!
65:
No matter how big she gets, she still
has the spirit of a little girl...
69:
Don't you think you should have
some fun out here too, Shirano?
73:
Come now, dearie. Someone like
me, frolicking on the beach...
78:
...No, you're right. I should set an
example.
79:
Come to this spot again tomorrow.
It's time I showed everyone what it
means to have fun in the sun.
91:
Whoa! Shirano, you are simply
RADIANT! What a stunner!
99:
Princess, Alk. Do you understand
what I've done here? It was quite
simple—
104:
No, I don't understand! I don't WANT
to!
108:
What does that outfit look like to
beastfolk?!
112:
Beats me. I grew up in a human
desert, remember? Besides, yokai
aren't beastfolk.
116:
This is... wrong, isn't it? Like I've
discovered a dark family secret...
122:
It seems I've managed to fluster
even our Alk.
125:
What's everyone freakin' out about
around here?
127:
Hold up! Who's this fox soakin' up
rays! You gotta be kidding me!
129:
Hey, baby! You lookin' for a guy
that'll treat you right—
137:
Now, lower your head and bare your
neck before me!
139:
Frail spirit. You will surrender yourself
to me! Speak, and make your
desires known!
141:
Ah... AHHH! P-please... Please... step
on me...
159: Why do you stop? Keep going!
166:
I'm simply showing you what a
yokai's love should look like.
169:
You would do well to remember this,
Princess.
178:
Although... I highly doubt you are
capable of such seductive tactics.
183: As mischievous as always, I see.
186: But of course! I am a fox, after all.
190:
That's enough for today, everyone.
Time for you all to go home.
194:
...Huh? What are we doing here,
again?
201:
U-um... Hey, uh... Fox lady! Could I
get your name?!
203:
You know, like... That coat you're
rockin' is so fine, you know? Heh...
205:
My, oh my! What do you say we get
out of here, young man?
215:
All riiight! I know a great place! This
guy named Scott runs the joint, and—
222:
H-hang on! Inaho! We can't just let
them go like that! Right?!
231:
Give it up, guys. None of your
business, right?
237: I cannot help but be intrigued!
241:
Same here! It's just called being
curious, Nimbus!
245:
Is this what she meant by "having
fun"?
